{"tid":853771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登尋她 朝早搭火車入一入","createTime":"2018-10-09T00:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T05:29:31.000Z","uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29e98b3544e98bb73a04ac9d8e1e41a0818d8dcd","tid":853771,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"10月9日 上午8:48<br />\n我搭緊火車去紅磡<br />\n我企係第一卡<br />\n見到有個好得意既女仔响到碌緊連燈<br />\n著灰色長西裝嬲 短boot（boot有啲鏈同鍋釘)<br />\n好靚好pure好想識佢<br />\n如果每日可以同佢一齊翻工保護佢等多人個時唔會俾啲西裝臭汗麻甩佬蹂躪<br />\n但毒撚唔敢開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7f8bc1904670e113b1fde9a5f5609056d0e1d8","tid":853771,"uid":60770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人想識你先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61c2e3d62e9e22b182217666488dd391094cd2f","tid":853771,"uid":187076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:57:09.000Z","msg":"原來係你個油頭毒撚望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c3b8a83ceedcc7b9a88d45de7d1ed00fcbdd7b","tid":853771,"uid":84128,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:58:06.000Z","msg":"其實我男人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢日突然興起著女裝<br />\n唔知你有冇興趣玩屎忽呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf9bbe32e0a080bb21b9557f0e3d16ee601f26f","tid":853771,"uid":72649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T01:00:12.000Z","msg":"佢轉左西鐵 我去搭過海巴士 <br />\n大家咁就消失係茫茫既人海<br />\n但有機會同一班車搭左幾個站都係今日既小確幸<br />\n祝大家有美好既一天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaa03fc2403f4b2779cab03ef5223a104bb0adf","tid":853771,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61c2e3d62e9e22b182217666488dd391094cd2f","tid":853771,"uid":187076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:57:09.